### 1. 测试用户注册 (Register)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. 测试用户登录 (Login)
# 登录成功后，请把返回的 token 复制下来
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. 测试获取当前用户信息 (Get Me)
